game_description: An expression of contemporary ideals, in a calming and nurturing environment. Show your love for high-quality materials with the premium cube, which includes: - A high-quality reflective cube - Polished metal hands (left & right) - A high quality cloudy skybox - A soft piano composition - Two unique hand gestures
